1.2.1	It is quite simple, actually.	St
1.2.2	You can use any number of manufacturers equipment and all are equally capable.	Ques
1.2.3	That includes DLink,Belkin and Linksys.	St
1.2.4	I am presently using Belkin and am pleased with it.	St
